<h3 style="background-color: #627f9a; color: white; padding-top: 10px; line-height: 28px; text-align: left;"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><strong>1500 Most Important Tamil Words With Meaning</strong></span></h3>
&nbsp;
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="width: 130px; background-color: #d99594; text-align: left;" colspan="4"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><strong id="bodyparts">1. BODY PARTS – உடல் உறுப்புகள் – UDAL URUPPUKAL</strong></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 10px; text-align: left; color: #0571c9; border: 2px solid #5579bf;"><strong>1</strong></td>
<td style="width: 60px; text-align: left; border: 2px solid #5579bf;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Abdomen</strong></span></td>
<td style="width: 60px; text-align: left; border: 2px solid #5579bf;"><span style="color: #0571c9;"><strong>அடி வயிறு</strong></span></td>
<td style="width: 60px; text-align: left; border: 2px solid #5579bf;"><span style="color: #0571c9;"><strong>Adi vayiru</strong></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 10px; text-align: left; color: #0571c9; border: 2px solid #5579bf;"><strong>2</strong></td>

<td style="width: 130px; background-color: #d99594; text-align: left;" colspan="4"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><strong id="bodyparts">1. BODY PARTS – உடல் உறுப்புகள் – UDAL URUPPUKAL</strong></span></td>
